<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='319000' id='t-319000'>You may think we can explain the Great Divergence</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='321000' id='t-321000'>in terms of geography.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='323000' id='t-323000'>We know that's wrong,</span>
