<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='467000' id='t-467000'>But you know, this is a TED audience,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='470000' id='t-470000'>and if I keep talking about institutions,</span>
