<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='525000' id='t-525000'>Let me very briefly tell you what I mean by this,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='528000' id='t-528000'>synthesizing the work of many economic historians</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='531000' id='t-531000'>in the process.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='533000' id='t-533000'>Competition means,</span>
