<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='575000' id='t-575000'>the most important being</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='577000' id='t-577000'>that, through the experimental method,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='579000' id='t-579000'>it gave men control over nature in a way that had not been possible before.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='582000' id='t-582000'>Example: Benjamin Robins's extraordinary application</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='586000' id='t-586000'>of Newtonian physics to ballistics.</span>
