<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='730000' id='t-730000'>Finally, the work ethic.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='732000' id='t-732000'>Max Weber thought that was peculiarly Protestant.</span>
